 12→>
 13→  <!-- Intro -->
 14→  <section class="intro">
 15→    <div class="intro-inner">
 16→      <h1>
 17→        <span class="intro-muted">We don't do everything. We do a few things very well.</span>{" "}
 18→        Strategy, design, and engineering for digital products.
 19→      </h1>
 20→    </div>
 21→  </section>
 22→
 23→  <!-- Services -->
 24→  <section class="services">
 25→    <div class="services-inner">
 26→      <div class="services-grid">
 27→        <article class="service-card">
 28→          <span class="service-number" aria-hidden="true">01</span>
 29→          <h2 class="service-title">Strategy</h2>
 30→          <p class="service-description">
 31→            Research, workshops, and roadmaps. Sometimes you need to step back before you build forward. We help you figure out
 32→            what to build and why — before a single pixel is pushed.
 33→          </p>
 34→          <ul class="service-details">
 35→            <li>User research</li>
 36→            <li>Product discovery</li>
 37→            <li>Technical audits</li>
 38→            <li>Roadmap planning</li>
 39→          </ul>
 40→        </article>
 41→
 42→        <article class="service-card">
 43→          <span class="service-number" aria-hidden="true">02</span>
 44→          <h2 class="service-title">Design</h2>
 45→          <p class="service-description">
 46→            UI, UX, branding, and prototyping. From first sketch to production-ready screens. Interfaces that are clear,
 47→            accessible, and built around real user needs — not assumptions.
 48→          </p>
 49→          <ul class="service-details">
 50→            <li>Product design</li>
 51→            <li>Interface design</li>
 52→            <li>Design systems</li>
 53→            <li>Prototyping</li>
 54→          </ul>
 55→        </article>
 56→
 57→        <article class="service-card">
 58→          <span class="service-number" aria-hidden="true">03</span>
 59→          <h2 class="service-title">Engineering</h2>
 60→          <p class="service-description">
 61→            Web, mobile, and infrastructure. We build what we design. Our stack choices serve the product, not the other way
 62→            around. Clean code, tested, ready for the real world.
 63→          </p>
 64→          <ul class="service-details">
 65→            <li>Web applications</li>
 66→            <li>Mobile apps</li>
 67→            <li>E-commerce</li>
 68→            <li>APIs & infrastructure</li>
 69→          </ul>
 70→        </article>
 71→      </div>
